RBS to Say 300 Bankers Paid $1.6 Million, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   K a r i   L u n d g r e n
-- 
2011-03-13T08:31:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/rbs-to-say-300-bankers-paid-1-6-million-sunday-times-reports.html
Royal Bank of Scotland Plc will say
next week it paid 300 of its senior managers salaries exceeding
1 million pounds ($1.6 million), the  Sunday Times  reported.  Total pay for executives will be about 350 million pounds,
the newspaper said, citing analysts. The bank is required to
disclose payments made to senior staff under new rules set by
the regulator, the paper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kari Lundgren in London at 
 klundgren2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:  Will Kennedy  at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net . 